      'about.cap.3.desc': 'Our analysts understand how reports will be used — in investment committee presentations, legal proceedings, regulatory filings, and board-level decisions. Reports are structured to meet the evidentiary standards of your specific use case.',
      'about.cap.4.title': 'Absolute Discretion',
      'about.cap.4.desc': 'Every engagement is confidential by default. We do not confirm or deny client relationships, we do not use client information for any purpose beyond the specific engagement, and all deliverables are transmitted through secure channels.',
      'about.sectors.eyebrow': 'Industries Served',
