      'contact.ethics.title': 'How We Handle Your Information',
      'contact.ethics.text': 'Every contact made to ISSLA Risk is protected under our Code of Ethics and handled with the same discretion we apply to our intelligence work. We do not share client information with third parties, do not disclose inquiry subjects, and do not retain personal data beyond the scope of the engagement.',
      'contact.ethics.link': 'Read Our Code of Ethics →',
